reviewText: If you know how to play pool, REALLY WELL, or know how to play piano, REALLY WELL, this video might have a useful nugget or two for you.  I can play a bit of piano (but am very mediocre at pool), and I found that most of this was beyond me.

An astounding DVD that shows the analogue in playing pool and the piano, with the credo of making both look easy--so that they become easy. Truly Zen in spirit, and exhibiting Milne's excellence in both arts.
